=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex55 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright noisy sound, with noise oscillator character around 53 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is early, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: early

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 53.2800
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0491
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0073
  pitch_clarity: 0.5757
  inharmonicity: 0.3356
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -8.9683
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 55
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 55 ---
(
{
    var z;
    z = Decay.ar(Dust.ar(1,0.5), 0.1, WhiteNoise.ar);
    8.do { z = AllpassL.ar(z, 0.04, 0.04.rand, 2) };
    z
}.play;
)
